# Pandorabots Landing Page {#landingpage}

_Now you can create a custom landing page for your chatbot in less than 5 minutes!_

Open your Pandorabots dashboard and expand the chatbot you wish to use. Select the Deploy menu option. 
This will display all the different channels and platforms you can use to connect your chatbot with. 

Click Setup for the Landing Page channel. This will open the design page template for you to customise 
how your landing page should look. You can now click and edit the various options to get it appearing just 
how you want.
 
</div>
